<form class="login">
    <mat-form-field class="full-width">
      <mat-label>Username</mat-label>
      <input matInput value="Username">
    </mat-form-field>
  
    <mat-form-field class="full-width">
      <mat-label>Password</mat-label>
      <input matInput type=password value="Password">
    </mat-form-field>
  </form>
